during promotional events.

Q: Can I use my Save-On-More keytag at Chevron?
A: You will need to use your FULL SIZE card with the
black magnetic stripe.
Q: What happens if I don't have my Save-On-More card
with me when I fuel up?
A: If you notify the Chevron cashier that you have
forgotten your card they will provide you with
Save-On-More points coupon(s) that can be
redeemed at any Save-On-Foods, Overwaitea
Foods, PriceSmart Foods, Cooper's Foods and
Urban Fare stores.
Every litre comes
with an added bonus.
Q: Can I use my Save-On-More Visa and my Save-On-More
Chevron
card at Chevron?
A: Yes. This is the fastest way to earn More Rewards.
ТЕСИRON
Q: What if my Save-On-More card can't be read at the
pump?
Check to ensure your Save-On-More card has a
black magnetic stripe. If it does and your card still
won't scan at the pump you can bring it inside the
station and the cashier can swipe it inside.
